{"tid":1082330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易戰】白宮：倘達協議美或取消部份華貨關稅","createTime":"2019-03-29T01:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T12:42:20.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e07ef83e9f3b4609a53d3d55b9e27c0469ea5a74","tid":1082330,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T01:28:45.000Z","msg":"中國和美國在北京展開新一輪貿易談判之際，美國白宮經濟顧問庫德洛（Larry Kudlow）周四透露，美國可能會取消對中國貨品加徵的某些關稅，同時保留其他關稅，以作為未來美、中貿易協議的執行機制之一。<br />\n<br />\n庫德洛出席美國進出口銀行（U.S.Export－Import Bank）年會期間對記者說：「我們必須看看執行情況如何，因此不會拋棄手中籌碼。不過要說明的是，這並不必然表示，所有關稅都會繼續課徵，只有部份關稅會保留。」<br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表萊特希澤（Robert Lighthizer）和財政部長姆努欽（Steven Mnuchcin）周四抵達北京，與中國官員進行新一輪貿易談判，下周雙方將在美國華府進行另一輪談判。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普上周曾表示，就算中美達成協議，中國貨品關稅仍可能維持一段長時間，確保中國遵守貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果動新聞》訂閱新世代，4月開始免費訂閱，現在接受登記！<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Ja3IXw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Ja3IXw&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=1b5a6484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Ja3IXw</a> <br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n《動腦Q》周末主題夜<br />\n追加星期六、日 9:30 pm<br />\n星期一至五 10:30 pm<br />\nDay Day Q the money!<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.adai.ly/veCxssynnV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.adai.ly%2FveCxssynnV&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=5b5a7677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.adai.ly/veCxssynnV</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190329/59424709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190329%2F59424709&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=836d658b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190329%2F59424709&h=90d36206\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190329/59424709</a>"},{"pid":"2cfe35e8293b1c1822ea23c25b122d7cc51eed37","tid":1082330,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T01:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由中興嗰陣已經成日用依招話「就緊傾好」嚟逼支那簽不平等條約"},{"pid":"1512fcb03f9172a50e248607950cca28894db127","tid":1082330,"uid":147079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:14:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c0f2300482b40c48dea94882d4232664fedbd55","tid":1082330,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:21:18.000Z","msg":"磨撚完未"},{"pid":"c3586a1e91db529ddbe65361ee1914934a08995a","tid":1082330,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c0f2300482b40c48dea94882d4232664fedbd55","tid":1082330,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:21:18.000Z","msg":"磨撚完未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:28:42.000Z","msg":"未到最後一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4418e731e3362e2da58bb6808a4e444457c5c28b","tid":1082330,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3586a1e91db529ddbe65361ee1914934a08995a","tid":1082330,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c0f2300482b40c48dea94882d4232664fedbd55","tid":1082330,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:21:18.000Z","msg":"磨撚完未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:28:42.000Z","msg":"未到最後一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:40:33.000Z","msg":"(下星期直取30000) 全球經貿戰：傳中美正「逐字逐句」檢查協議內容<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1082925\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1082925</a><br />\n<br />\n同你一隻一隻字對呀 屌你 今次唔撚比你走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a13fb395b9d795201f552d5d79a6b415152016b","tid":1082330,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot